description:
Hi,

A spring view of the Slovak Belianske Tatras, and above them the spring Milky Way! The highest visible peak is Hawra≈Ñ - the highest peak of the Belianske Tatras in Slovakia, located in the central part of their western half, in the main ridge of the Tatra Mountains, on the section where it coincides with the main ridge of the Belianske Tatras; at the same time, the highest limestone peak of the entire Tatra Mountains. 

Parameters:

Category: tracked/ stacked / blended:
Canon 6D mod and Sigma 40mm f1.4 ART
Sky: Pano 2 x 120s ISO800 @ f2.8
Foreground: Pano 2 x 120s ISO800 @ f2.8
title: Belianske Tatras and the Milky Way 10/05/2021
